Western Atlantic – 
<collectingCountry box="[575,643,1396,1420]" name="Brazil" pageId="8" pageNumber="34">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(Fernando de Noronha and from Pará to Bahia).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,1143,1528]" box="[199,1295,1431,1456]" pageId="8" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,298,1431,1456]" pageId="8" pageNumber="34">Habitat.</emphasis>
